Package com.st.st25sdk.command

Defines methods to build the commands for: Iso7816, Iso14443, Iso15693, NFC Forum type 4, NFC Forum type 5, Vicinity including high level commands for NDEF messages

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    Iso14443aCommandInterface  
    Iso14443SRCustomCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build SO14443-B SR commands
    Iso15693CommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build ISO15693/NFC Forum type5 commands
    Iso15693CustomCommandInterface
    Defines the methods to build STMicroelectronics ISO15693 custom commands
    Iso15693CustomKillCommandInterface
    This interface defines all Kill functions
    NdefCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build read and write NFC Forum NDEF messages
    Type4CommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build NFC Forum Type4 commands
    Type4CustomCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build STMicroelectronics Type4 Tag commands
    Type5CommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build Type5 commands
    Type5MemoryCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build Type5 Memory commands
    VicinityCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to build Vicinity commands (specific format commands for M24LR16E, M24LR64E, LRIS64K = 2 bytes address)
    VicinityMemoryCommandInterface
    Defines the common methods to be implemented to manage Vicinity Memory commands (specific format commands for M24LR16E, M24LR64E, LRIS64K = 2 bytes address)
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    FastTransferModeCommand
    Defines methods to build the Fast Transfer Mode commands related to MailBox management (Fast Transfer Mode)

    Defines methods to build Iso44443-3 and Iso44443-4 commands
    Iso14443SRCustomCommand
    Defines methods to build all the ISO14443-B SR commands
    Iso15693Command
    Defines methods to build Iso15693 commands
    Iso15693CustomCommand
    Defines methods to build the STMicroelectronics Iso15693 custom commands
    Iso15693Protocol
    Defines methods for the high level methods for ISO15693 protocol
    Iso7816Command
    Defines methods to build the ISO7816 commands
    Iso7816Type4RApduStatus
    Defines methods to manage the Type4 ISO7816 R-APDU status
    NdefType4Command
    Defines methods to build commands to work with NFC Forum Type4 NDEF messages
    NdefType5Command
    Defines methods to build commands to work with NFC Forum Type5 NDEF messages
    NdefVicinityCommand
    Defines methods to build commands to work with NFC Forum Type5 NDEF messages adapted to Vicinity tags
    Type4Command
    Defines methods to build all the NFC Forum Type4 commands
    Type4CustomCommand
    Defines methods to build STMicroelectronics Type4 tags commands
    Type5Command
    Defines methods to manage the high level methods for Type5 tags
    Type5MemoryCommand
    The Type5MemoryCommand class implements some high level methods such as : the readBlocks/Bytes() and writeBlocks/Bytes() methods of Iso15693Command for Iso15693 tags whatever the tag memory size
    VicinityCommand
    Defines methods to build the Vicinity commands (specific format commands for M24LR16E, M24LR64E, LRIS64K = 2 bytes address)
    VicinityMemoryCommand
    The VicinityMemoryCommand class implements some high level methods such as readBlocks/Bytes() and writeBlocks/Bytes() methods for Vicinity tags whatever the tag memory size
